ğŸ¯ Project Insights

Some examples of insights (your notebook may vary):

Netflix has added more content in recent years compared to earlier decades.

Movies dominate the platform compared to TV Shows.

United States and India contribute the highest number of titles.

The most common rating is TV-MA, indicating adult-focused content.

Drama and International movies are among the most frequent genres.
